medications.name: Sertraline
medications.response: Suboptimal/Partial response noted after 4 weeks on 50mg; dosage increased.

changes_made.rationale: Patient reported persistent moderate depressive symptoms (anhedonia, guilt, early morning awakening, passive ideation) and minimal symptomatic relief after 4 weeks on the starting dose of 50mg. Dose titrated from 50mg to 100mg daily.
